item.title: Resume
item.description: Alexandre Normand Canadian Citizen, USA Green Card Holder • Github • Contact info provided separately Profile I'm an experienced remote Java and Go developer with a great passion for making small differences in this world. I'm most comfortable writing backend but I'm willing and able to work on anything in order to reach a goal. I also like to make remote work fun and friendly using the incredible power of gifs and old school textual humor.
